description:
This is a 13 minute workout called '13 min Breathwork & Meditation Practice | Pranayama Techniques | Stress & Anxiety Relief' from the channel Akshaya Agnes.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.
